miso.carrascal.cloudModelServices

Class MongoDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • miso.carrascal.cloudModelServices.MongoDB
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InterfaceDB

    public class MongoDB
extends java.lang.Object
implements InterfaceDB
    Custom implementation of and non-relational mongo database. It uses com.mongodb.gridfs.GridFS to store files. It creates one com.mongodb.DBCollection for each Persistent class stored.
    Author:
    Carlos Carrascal.
